item.title: Changes are afoot
item.description: For the last year or so I have been working on a MacBook Air. This was fine when all I was doing was writing but as I am doing coding I was finding the small screen size to be limiting. So yesterday I went our and bought a 24" monitor, a stand for the MacBook and an Anker USB C port to allow the MacBook to drive the monitor.
